{"tid":2299614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"目前只有警務處安排文職員工分組上班 大多政府部門未有跟隨最新建議","createTime":"2020-11-25T02:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T03:41:23.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3b983bf72f7b159d8a1d1c3f704a85bc250092","tid":2299614,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:33:47.000Z","msg":"梁籌庭：很多政府部門未有安排員工居家工作<br />\n<br />\n公務員工會聯合會總幹事梁籌庭指，公務員事務局就部門彈性上班的指引，並非硬性執行，據他了解，目前只有警務處安排文職員工分組返回辦公室工及孕婦居家工作，很多部門未有安排只得一半員工返回辦公室工作，希望政府向各部門發出清晰指引。<br />\n<br />\n梁籌庭在一個電台節目表示，政府部門的工作並非大部份可以回家處理，執行上有難度，返回辦公室員工會無償加班，措施未必受員工歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n梁籌庭指，政府與私人機構很大分別，私人機構有更大彈性，希望因應政府呼籲，安排員工居家工作。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2367788\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2367788&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=a2b316fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2367788</a>"},{"pid":"d123a3c5abd004c78f2f461077c9c3ca1932a9e0","tid":2299614,"uid":2959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:36:00.000Z","msg":"連公務員都冇聽政府話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />算吧啦"},{"pid":"3520b4e7f2e5b28c6643fd4aab6e5df0a170715f","tid":2299614,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:36:39.000Z","msg":"支持支持"},{"pid":"0665be1e831ea536e309694e90458e26234d9948","tid":2299614,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:36:53.000Z","msg":"私人機構有更大彈性，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f2ebdbf54f1f0570364ed37c5e7e07433dca53","tid":2299614,"uid":51057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:37:20.000Z","msg":"肯定唔只曱甴屋有wfh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1290ca42f3b8c4f410025770d22b1dfae77d5b94","tid":2299614,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":